title: Ep - 49 - INSIDE PRODUCTION SECRETS FROM BELOW DECK, REAL HOUSEWIVES OF MIAMI, AND MORE
description:
Nadine Rajabi, Executive Producer of Bravo’s Below Deck Med and producer for shows including Real Housewives of Miami , Jerseylicious, There Goes The Motherhood, Bravo’s Game of Crowns, and Most Eligible: Dallas gives production secrets. Luann De Lessep’s ex-boyfriend Rey from Real Housewives of New York gives his thoughts about her divorce. Matt Snively, a married husband in Kansas City, Missouri reviews the new show So Sharp on Lifetime about a dance team coach and Grace Lally, a 25 year old startup sales professional in New York City reviews MTV’s new show Siesta Key.
